### Entity Relationship Summary

```
organizations 1--* alert_channels      (orgId FK)
organizations 1--* agent_risk_snapshots (orgId FK, nullable)
users         1--* agent_risk_snapshots (userId FK, nullable)
cloud_accounts     + scan_schedule (text)
cloud_accounts     + next_scan_at  (text, nullable)
```

### Index Strategy

| Table | Index | Columns | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| alert_channels | idx_alert_channels_org | org_id | List channels by org |
| alert_channels | idx_alert_channels_org_active | org_id, is_active | Filter active channels for dispatch |
| agent_risk_snapshots | idx_risk_snapshots_user_date | user_id, snapshot_date | User trend queries |
| agent_risk_snapshots | idx_risk_snapshots_org_date | org_id, snapshot_date | Org trend queries |
| agent_risk_snapshots | idx_risk_snapshots_user_date_unique | user_id, snapshot_date (unique partial) | Prevent duplicate snapshots per user per day |
| agent_risk_snapshots | idx_risk_snapshots_org_date_unique | org_id, snapshot_date (unique partial) | Prevent duplicate snapshots per org per day |

